data.description: THIS BEAUTIFUL CABIN SITS ON ALMOST 1 ACRE OF HEAVILY TREED LAND IN A PRESTIGOUS GATED COMMUNITY. Community has a beautiful clubhouse within walking distance, & subdivision has a stellar appearance.  This 4 bdrm/3 bath has so much to offer.  Huge upgraded open kitchen with beautiful Alder cabinets, granite countertops & an amazing kitchen island.  Beautiful 2 side fireplace separates dining/kitchen area and great room.  Home is equipped with a propane back fed Generac generator.  This stunning floor plan is a single level split floor plan for privacy, 3 guestrooms for family. Vaulted ceilings, large windows, bay windows and 8 ft doors make this a great spacious open feeling throughout.   .SELLER HAS LOT NEXT DOOR TO BE SOLD SEP FOR $50K
